===============================================================================

Now you must do some setup manually if you haven't yet:

  1. Add bootstrap.min.css to your application.css file:
      
      *= require bootstrap/bootstrap.min.css
      
  2. Add bootstrap javascript files to your application.js file:
      
      //= require_tree ../../../vendor/assets/javascripts/bootstrap/
      
    Or do it separately:
      
      //= require bootstrap/bootstrap-alerts.js
      //= require bootstrap/bootstrap-dropdown.js
      //= require bootstrap/bootstrap-modal.js
      //= require bootstrap/bootstrap-twipsy.js
      //= require bootstrap/bootstrap-popover.js
      //= require bootstrap/bootstrap-scrollspy.js
      //= require bootstrap/bootstrap-tabs.js

===============================================================================
